/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盃又少過奧燒 幾隻有返d份量嘅盃都係巴塞果陣坐出黎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n數劇又輸幾條街 巔峰又得兩三年<br />\n計依家又輸 計成個生涯都輸 話兩個同級咪算比臉佢嘅球技"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:38:06.000Z","msg":"講多少少<br />\n點解咁多阿狗明叔 德國明叔咁鍾意罵奧燒？<br />\n係咪只係針對？ 佢無問題？<br />\n佢踢阿咁耐 得一季英超助攻係雙位數（就係佢助攻王果季）<br />\n其餘時間單位數<br />\n你咁鍾意講數字 佢係咪地球助攻王？<br />\n舊年阿英超無望 佢又成日射波唔使踢<br />\n專心踢歐霸<br />\n點知對馬體會又係食屎級表現<br />\n之後季尾英超一場無出過<br />\n留力世界杯？<br />\n點知世界杯又係食屎級表現<br />\n比全國屌到退出德國國家隊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b084095f277057dadbb3ead6b7cf41d4ce05390","tid":1110061,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b2303fde09e30783b646b7d306fc53ff0ff1f7f","tid":1110061,"uid":73536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T11:50:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429c49fc38efeaa9c88ef8966f1285b517607985","tid":1110061,"uid":73536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:46:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a016890085cc89a6df2cdee8a6d19951b9a2b9c7","tid":1110061,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"429c49fc38efeaa9c88ef8966f1285b517607985","tid":1110061,"uid":73536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b084095f277057dadbb3ead6b7cf41d4ce05390","tid":1110061,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b2303fde09e30783b646b7d306fc53ff0ff1f7f","tid":1110061,"uid":73536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T11:50:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:46:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:00:41.000Z","msg":"綠在骨子裡"},{"pid":"d0851439bdc59aa2eb78a7d4